  <Summary>IDW Publishing teams up with Gold Eagle to reprise one of adventure fiction&#8217;s longest-running novel series: Don Pendleton's Mack Bolan, The Executioner! The inspiration for countless payback warrior characters since 1969, Bolan returns in an explosive five-issue miniseries that pits him against enemies drawn from the Executioner's many novelized conflicts&#8212;from his war against the Mafia to his battles with the KGB and even today&#8217;s terrorists! By celebrated author Douglas Wojtowicz, writer of many of The Executioner novels, with art by S.L. Gallant (Johnny Quest) and a cover by Rogue Angel cover artist Rebecca A. Wrigley.</Summary>
